title: Fantasy Draft Redo + Ride or Die, TNF Preview - Fantasy Football Podcast for 10/12
description:
Get ready for Week 6! On today’s fantasy football podcast, a two-round fantasy draft redo! Andy, Mike, and Jason take turns picking the top 24 players for rest of season. Plus a preview of Thursday Night Football between the Commanders and Bears and a new edition of “Ride or Die!” Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for October 12th, 2022.
